    summary: "List your photography services on the Fotiqo marketplace to reach new clients. Apply and get approved to start receiving bookings.",
    content: "## Steps\n\n1. Go to Settings > Marketplace and click Join Marketplace.\n2. Read and accept the marketplace terms and conditions.\n3. Complete your marketplace application with your photography specialties.\n4. Upload at least 10 portfolio images that represent your best work.\n5. Set up at least one booking package with pricing.\n6. Configure your service area and travel radius.\n7. Submit your application for review.\n8. You will receive an approval decision within 1 to 3 business days.\n\n**\u{1F4A1} Tip:** Applications with strong portfolios and complete profiles are approved faster. Put your best foot forward.\n\n## FAQ\n\n**Q: What are the requirements to join?**\nA: You need a complete profile, at least 10 portfolio images, one active package, and a connected Stripe account.\n\n**Q: Is the marketplace available worldwide?**\nA: Yes, the marketplace is available in all countries where Stripe is supported.\n\n**Q: Can I leave the marketplace later?**\nA: Yes, you can deactivate your marketplace listing at any time without affecting your account.\n\n## Related Articles\n- [How to set up your marketplace profile](/help/marketplace-profile-setup)\n- [How to create marketplace packages](/help/marketplace-packages)\n- [How to set availability for marketplace bookings](/help/marketplace-availability)",
